## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-102">這個類別提供應用程式可以處理所說的使用者輸入文字的預先定義的語言模型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-102">This class provides applications with a predefined language model that can process spoken user input into text.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-103">此類別支援預設和自訂<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-103">This class supports both default and custom <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-104">如需選取聽寫文法的詳細資訊，請參閱<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.%23ctor%28System.String%29>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-104">For information about selecting a dictation grammar, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.%23ctor%28System.String%29> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-105">根據預設，<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar>語言模型是免費的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-105">By default, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> language model is context free.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-106">它不會使用特定單字或單字找出並解譯音訊輸入的順序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-106">It does not make use of specific words or word order to identify and interpret audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-107">若要將內容加入至聽寫文法中，使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.SetDictationContext%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-107">To add context to the dictation grammar, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.SetDictationContext%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-108"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> 物件不支援<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.Priority%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-108"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> objects do not support the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.Priority%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> 會擲回<xref:System.NotSupportedException>如果<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.Priority%2A>設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar> throws a <xref:System.NotSupportedException> if <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.Priority%2A> is set.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-110">下列範例會建立三個的聽寫文法，然後將它們新增至新<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>物件，並傳回新的物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-110">The following example creates three dictation grammars, adds them to a new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object, and returns the new object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-111">第一個文法是預設聽寫文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-111">The first grammar is the default dictation grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-112">第二個文法是拼字的聽寫文法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-112">The second grammar is the spelling dictation grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-113">第三個文法是預設聽寫文法，其中包含內容的片語。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-113">The third grammar is the default dictation grammar that includes a context phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="fd9af-114"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.SetDictationContext%2A>方法來操作片語關聯聽寫文法之後載入，以<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="fd9af-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.DictationGrammar.SetDictationContext%2A> method is used to associate the context phrase with the dictation grammar after it is loaded to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine LoadDictationGrammars()  
{  
  
  // Create a default dictation grammar.  
  DictationGrammar defaultDictationGrammar = new DictationGrammar();  
  defaultDictationGrammar.Name = "default dictation";  
  defaultDictationGrammar.Enabled = true;  
  
  // Create the spelling dictation grammar.  
  DictationGrammar spellingDictationGrammar =  
    new DictationGrammar("grammar:dictation#spelling");  
  spellingDictationGrammar.Name = "spelling dictation";  
  spellingDictationGrammar.Enabled = true;  
  
  // Create the question dictation grammar.  
  DictationGrammar customDictationGrammar =  
    new DictationGrammar("grammar:dictation");  
  customDictationGrammar.Name = "question dictation";  
  customDictationGrammar.Enabled = true;  
  
  // Create a SpeechRecognitionEngine object and add the grammars to it.  
  SpeechRecognitionEngine recoEngine = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  recoEngine.LoadGrammar(defaultDictationGrammar);  
  recoEngine.LoadGrammar(spellingDictationGrammar);  
  recoEngine.LoadGrammar(customDictationGrammar);  
  
  // Add a context to customDictationGrammar.  
  customDictationGrammar.SetDictationContext("How do you", null);  
  
  return recoEngine;  
}  
  
```
